('11111111-0011-0011-0011-000000000011', 'LinkedinLens', ARRAY['marketing','ai'], '$18k/mo', '3.1k', 'ih', 'https://indiehackers.com/linkedinlens', 'Overlays competitor signals on LinkedIn profiles for sales reps. Average ACV $49/mo, churn ~3%.', 'yes', 'complex', '2026-05-12 00:00:00+00'),
